A complete, object-oriented chess implementation written in python3 using the pygame library.

All official chess rules and mechanics are supported.

To run the app, from the src/ directory, run:

  $ python3 chess.py
  
DEPENDENCIES: pygame

To install pygame with pip3, run:

  $ pip3 install pygame

DEMO: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLDlLzU2EysQjMh3X1WvNVpr9O8uaTgdSv

NOTE: The pygame package may not be compatible with MacOS Mojave and attempting to run any program
      using it may result in an infinite loop. More info about this issue and a potential fix can be 
      found here: https://github.com/pygame/pygame/issues/555
